{"tid":1555763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online每日任務系統出左啦","createTime":"2019-09-09T13:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:40:15.000Z","uid":92277,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"77b67dc2f7b93118e0c81e506056033be7e677c0","tid":1555763,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">多謝大家唔想我用錢唔推我個5000蚊post... 依家重開一個，求人手置頂</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗唔係無人撐，係因為無人知，靠你比所有人知</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文宣我認為係難道最低而又可以幫到成個運動既一件事。<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實整圖既巴打唔介意人地偷圖，只會怪人睇完唔forward! </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔識整圖既大家，我有三樣野希望大家幫幫手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.分享去 Facebook IG Whatsapp Gp </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n難聽講句，IG story輕鬆都百幾二百人睇啦！連登接觸面唔係唔廣，但可以再廣啲，而且留得係到既已經係跟得好貼既人。希望大家見到靚既文宣，由其<span style=\"color: red;\">行動post</span>，幫一幫手做多步，repost 埋上ig, facebook, WhatsApp 之類既社交評台。一人拉多一個人去遊行就已經多好多。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<br />\n200萬人有幾多個真係睇連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542401\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 貼連儂牆</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然依家科技發達，但仲有好多人無辦法係果到收到信息。平時我等車都會望到好多叔叔望下牆。其實佢真係好吸睛，都係直接文宣既好地方!<br />\n<br />\n**建議組隊進行，放工放學咪貼兩張。<br />\n**如要去廠印刷，落單要開新Account <br />\n<br />\n原post:<br />\n老母一句屌醒左我，駁唔到。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546699\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n文宣組入！印刷都會出事！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dPQbDT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dPQbDT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. Airdrop 比全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n0成本，直接塞信息比人，<span style=\"color: red;\">行動post 優先</span>。平時搭車，行街得閒無野做咪用下！<br />\n<br />\n原post: <br />\n<br />\nIPhone有個咁好用既功能點解要浪費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551471\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551471</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.分享呢個post</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n剩係得你睇到係唔夠嫁，我想全部人都知點做，打工仔知點做，撐我地既哥哥姐姐知點做！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣，係無大台既我地最重要既一環！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ld9NuBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLd9NuBN.jpg&h=2115e932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzQQsos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzQQsos.jpg&h=35463d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUOniu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUOniu8.jpg&h=ad130f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！光復之日，煲底相聚💛</span>"},{"pid":"651b34fbbf7ff6781717be2e9bd361711940800b","tid":1555763,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:01:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efd52d754f7f00521b5f9e52ee5a5d754dac6f8e","tid":1555763,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:02:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ff966cbf8470c3a795626ff857e53f43a6eff4a","tid":1555763,"uid":92277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:03:36.000Z","msg":"低成本高效益<br />\n貼紙洗得幾多錢？<br />\n<br />\n今日放工有個叔叔指住牆話：&ldquo;9月23罷工喎&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n佢朋友：&ldquo;定9月2同3&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我：係2同3呀，多謝支持先<br />\n<br />\n佢：下次早啲講嘛<br />\n<br />\n文宣呀！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"465fd50c41728c2e5b1c19ce2e0093f2d737d9ba","tid":1555763,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"認同請轉發 謝謝"